TSSr example data

exampleTSSr.Rd

Subset of the CAGE dataset from the paper Lu and Lin, Genome Research 2019 Jul;29(7):1198-1210.

data(exampleTSSr)

Format

An object of class TSSr

exampleTSSr

RangedSummarizedExperiment:TSSr

Source

https://genome.cshlp.org/content/29/7/1198.short

Examples
